Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:41.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:52.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:59.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:06.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:13.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:17.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:27.76,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:34.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:41.21,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:52.69,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:39.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能换人不再悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:41.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我宁愿舍弃笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:45.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}她说着低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:52.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这一夜 我流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:59.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冰冷彻骨 仿如冻雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:06.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}洒落的现实 无处可避
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:13.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:17.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅为这理由而束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Heart  My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:27.76,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪光对面 看到了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:34.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的窗上 映出旧时晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:41.21,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽无法如鸟儿一般飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:54.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为铭记谁人悲伤之时的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}轻轻闭上双眼 哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:58.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}なくす事が拾うためなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:04.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}別れるのは出逢うため
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:09.55,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}「さようなら」のあとには　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:15.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}「こんにちは」と出逢うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:26.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}緑色芝生に寝ころんでいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:37.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}動物も一緒にゴロゴロしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:45.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}今日は良い事がたくさんあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:58.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}若失去是为了寻回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:04.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}别离就是为了相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:09.55,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}告别之后 一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:15.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}邂逅你的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:26.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}多想躺在那翠绿草坪上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:37.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}和动物们一同撒欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:45.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs19}若今日顺心如意…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是电磁场光共振部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如其名 狙击！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认卫星武器被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密已脱离战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是天人的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E探测器有反应 是敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏了Memento Mori就要付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:12.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(152,360)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}歌声传来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静止卫星轨道上发生的爆炸事故
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已查明为反联邦势力攻击所为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为应对日渐残暴的恐怖行为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦议会已将联邦军置于独立治安维持部队直属之下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行全世界规模的防卫网强化…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento Mori被击毁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中的KATARON势力基本都扫清了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要统一世界实现持久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须想尽办法摧毁天人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若对其放任自流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府势力很可能卷土重来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汇合地点应该是这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机体是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 好久不见 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 变得好帅哦 妮娜小鹿乱撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢着 刚才我不是救了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你们的舰船好像落到地球上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把战斗资料传给你 看了就知道去向…哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用急成这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是急性子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了 被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是吹的什么风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟大老远跑来中东找我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有情报要告知身负军方监查任务的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军中有人在策划政变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道不少人对联邦政府的政策抱持反感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但政变实在是出乎意料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府已沦为A-LAWS的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须唤醒民众
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟尔盖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力? 几时到地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这咋回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反监视用光学迷彩恢复 立即展开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 虽然启动了00-Raiser 击退了拉格朗日3的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知A-LAWS使用了卫星兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便立即转入破坏其武器的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽顺利击毁 却遭到敌方奇袭而降落地球圈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地面紧急迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还和刹那驾驶的00-Raiser分散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全正确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们破坏了卫星武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在GN粒子耗尽时遭遇了奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上敌方部队还投入了新型MA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用舰船中弹所受的冲击进行加速
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用烟雾隐藏船体降落地面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若没有皇·李·诺列嘉这随机应变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必败无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着就是奇迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 托勒密现在什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎倒是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航行系统及武器管制 通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测器之类都损伤严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样 这种时候要是遇到敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我送饭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从容过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让玛丽小姐也参战了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且玛丽自己同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 希望不要再有第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然破坏了卫星武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这边损失也不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若情况不妙 将要借助支部的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和谁通话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点私事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS为何能如此正确地掌握普特莱玛奥斯的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:09:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 雷特纳尔小姐是在怀疑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 只是有些疑问而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 叫我艾纽就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也叫我莱尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·狄兰提 是我的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密的反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是卫星武器的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也都是变革者安置的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 那家伙怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军中部分人在策划政变?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 池田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报来源是我做记者时的旧友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了A-LAWS的恶行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政变派打算接触我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉地点指定在中东
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 克劳斯 可能是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他们希望端正联邦恶政的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且应该给予回应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像是玛莉娜皇女收集孩子们所说的话 创作的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下还唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方向是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 久违了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经是库尔吉斯的小哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又投靠变革者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 佣兵只认钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的战斗毫无意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 但说了你也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有人想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的主顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫利冯兹 利冯兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰·易卜拉欣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 你是第一次见我来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11年前我就遇见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人类之间相互杀戮的泥沼般的战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位少年在绝望地挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从MS的驾驶舱中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Gundam上的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次武力介入是0 Gundam的性能试验
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然为保守机密 在场者原本都应被处死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你凝视着0 Gundam和我的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人印象深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 通过Veda将你推荐为Gundam Meister的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我道谢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的职责已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该物归原主了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台机体原本就是属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意射失?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将 我的生活目的是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 请便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 两台不明MS从不同方向袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 让阿勒路亚和提耶利亚出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的位置暴露了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee 提耶利亚·艾迪 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios 阿勒路亚·哈普提森
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤了还能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮击型 想射没门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算哈雷路亚不在!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大气层中对方机动性占优吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你有Veda撑腰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚·艾迪 你是 变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们共同完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是变革者的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争正在扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能让大家听到我们的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽不忍心射杀同类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但必须履行使命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也有不能退让之处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Field?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM吗 这种程度的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Nadleeh当初不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此番登场乃有意为之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seraphim Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Seraphim:六翼天使）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对同类也要下手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人类！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林·斯塔比利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 有MS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来护航的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就算是人质了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖别动…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:57.71,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}なくす事が拾うためなら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:03.30,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}別れるのは出逢うため
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}「さようなら」のあとには　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:14.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}「こんにちは」と出逢うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:25.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}緑色芝生に寝ころんでいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:36.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}動物も一緒にゴロゴロしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:48.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}今日は良い事がたくさんあったから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:59.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日も良い事がたくさんあるように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:04.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}お日様出て　夕日きれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:10.25,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}星に願い明日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:15.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}どうして行っちゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:21.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一緒に帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:57.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs19}如果丢失是为找回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:03.30,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs19}离别是为邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs19}「再见」之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:14.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs19}会遇见「你好」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:25.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs19}多想躺在那翠绿草坪上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:36.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}和动物们一同撒欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:48.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}若今日顺心如意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:59.20,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}祈祷明天也会好事多多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:04.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}太阳公公升起来 夕阳美如画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:10.25,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}向星星祈愿明天会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:15.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}为什么要走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:21.85,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是新型机
